Description: Functions for deconvolution of 1D NMR spectra followed by alignment of the data and some additional post-processing resulting in a data matrix of aligned signal integrals. The deconvolution part uses the code base of 'MetaboDecon1D' (<doi:10.3390/metabo11070452>). The alignment is done using functions from the 'speaq' package (<https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=speaq>).
